Package org.ietf.nea.pa.message

IETF integrity measurement message implementation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PaMessageHeaderBuilder
    Generic builder to build an integrity measurement component message header compliant to RFC 5792.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultImMessageContainer
    Default helper object to pass on an integrity measurement component message and minor validation errors after parsing for further processing.

    IETF RFC 5792 integrity measurement message.

    IETF RFC 5792 integrity measurement message header.
